Panic At The Disco - Too Weird to Live, Too Rare to Die! [2013] Album
Fueled By Ramen / CD
MP3 V0 VBR

Fourth studio album by American rock band Panic! at the Disco. Musically, the album is inspired by hip-hop in that "there are no rules." In an extension of that mantra, the album is an eclectic affair that varies wildly from song to song.
